Multiple Environment sample

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 $ git clone git://github.com/bluepapa32/gradle-environment-sample.git
 $ git checkout 20110310
 $ cd gradle-environment-sample

 =========================
  Use default environment
 =========================
 $ ./gradlew -q
 http://app:8080/setting


 ===================
  Use the -P option
 ===================
 $ ./gradlew -q -Penv=test
 http://app:8080/setting


 =========================================
  Use the GRADLE_ENV environment variable
 =========================================
 $ GRADLE_ENV=production ./gradlew -q
 https://app/setting


 =====================================
  Use $HOME/.gradle/gradle.properties
 =====================================
 $ echo "env=test" >> $HOME/.gradle/gradle.properties 
 $ ./gradlew -q
 http://app:8080/setting

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
